content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 8122.36 - Town of Pamelia

State Regulations
(a) Route 37. The northbound and southbound roadways of Route 37, between the intersection of

Route 342 and a point 0.2+- mile south of Route 342 in the Town of

Pamelia. (b) Route 342. Route 342
between IR 81 and the Jefferson County Residency, a distance of 0.7+-
mile. (c) Route 12. Route 12
between northbound IR 81 and the most northerly intersection of Murrock Circle
with Route 12. (d) Murrock Circle. Murrock Circle between its most northerly and most southerly intersection with

Route 12. Notes
